作者姓名(中文):林楷崴作者姓名(英文):Kai-Wei Lin論文名稱(中文):基於共享經濟與物聯網技術之適地性二手物品交易平臺論文名稱(外文):Location-based Second-hand exchange platform by implementing sharing economy and IoT technique指導教授姓名(中文):楊亦東指導教授姓名(英文):I-Tung Yang口試委員姓名(中文):陳柏翰陳鴻銘口試委員姓名(英文):Po-Han ChenHung-Ming Chen學位類別:碩士校院名稱:國立臺灣科技大學系所名稱:營建工程系學號:M10305506出版年(民國):105畢業學年度:104學期:2語文別:中文論文頁數:105中文關鍵詞:物聯網、共享經濟、電子商務、適地性服務、無線射頻辨識外文關鍵詞:Internet of Things、Sharing economy、Electronic Commerce、Location-Based Service、Radio Frequency Identification相關次數:

推薦:0點閱:22評分:下載:0收藏:0



科技帶給人類更多便利。隨著資通訊科技的快速發展與普及，物聯網的時代隨之而來。人的日常生活作息和人與人之間的關係，已經與資訊科技密不可分，智慧家庭帶給人們更智慧的生活。智慧家庭在偵測環境或是智慧化的節約能源都已相當的成熟，但對外沒有一個開放的入口讓家庭與家庭之間能互動。本研究基於共享經濟之概念，運用Android系統智慧型手機與物聯網開發晶片作為開發環境，並建置一個智慧家庭對外開放的平臺，透過手機應用程式和RFID（Radio Frequency Identification）標籤與家庭物聯網裝置溝通，推播訊息給經過家庭實體位置的使用者手機，運用此方式達成適地性的服務，讓家庭可以與路人或附近鄰居互動。使每個家庭能銷售或租借家中的閒置品。家庭不再是只有消費者的角色，更能促使共享經濟之推廣，從而透過人際分享與互動信任來減少浪費與促進經濟發展。

Smart home devices that change daily life and bring more convenience to modern people have been encouraged when it comes to environment detection and automatic energy saving; however, the present applications lack an open channel for the interaction between families. With the rapid growth of information technology and the widespread use of Internet of Things (IoT), the communication patterns of people and the inter-relationship also evolved. This study , based on the concept of sharing economy, employs Android phones and open-source hardware for IoT devices as the development environment to construct a virtual window for each family. The proposed system uses radio frequency identification (RFID) and WiFi to be the communication means. The proposed system is location-based, so the family can sell or rent out the redundant items to neighbors and passers who are interested. In such a way, a family is not only a consumer but can also be part of sharing economy. By promoting interpersonal sharing and interactive trust, the proposed system intends to raise social value, reduce waste, and boost economic development.

